pageContext.claim: “This was a steel ramp, it had no handrail. It was like an ice skating rink....And then, we finally reached almost the end and the fake news, the most dishonest human beings, they cut it off. Do you know why? Because when I was 10 feet short, I said, General -- I'm sorry, and I ran down the rest, right?”
pageContext.analysis: It was a beautiful day at West Point and reporters said the ramp did not appear wet, let alone like an "ice skating rink."
